<p class="en" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Sources: Finbold and CryptoTimes (bitcoin price and volume, July 6, 2026), crypto.news (the ETF's eighth consecutive week of net outflows and weekly data), TechTimes and CoinDesk (ETF flow tallies), Strategy's 8-K filing, and CoinGlass (futures open interest, trading volume, and liquidation data as of July 6, 2026). Figures are approximate, per reporting and aggregator data.</p>
